videos.description: Braxton Beverly comes off a screen and hooks a pass to Wyatt Walker, who rises up for the big two-handed finish at the rim.
videos.headline: NC State's Beverly feeds Walker for two-handed jam

videos.description: Nikola Djogo drives baseline and gets around DJ Funderburk, taking off for the rim and throwing down a strong two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Djogo drives and dunks for Notre Dame

videos.description: Eric Lockett sends a pass to the rim for DJ Funderburk, who catches and finishes with a rim-rocking two-handed flush.
videos.headline: Funderburk throws down big alley-oop for Wolfpack

videos.description: Prentiss Hubb comes off the screen and makes a beautiful pass down low to John Mooney, who finishes the play with a two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Notre Dame's Hubb feeds Mooney for two-handed flush

videos.description: Jericole Hellems picks off Nate Laszewski's pass and takes it the length of the floor, finishing at the rim to extend the Wolfpack's lead to 69-63.
videos.headline: NC State's Hellems steals and scores
